w.nme.com/news/music/oasis-are-preparing-to-cancel-more-than-50000-tickets-sold-via-secondary-ticket-sites-3807274">取消通过转售网站出售的数千张即将举行的 2025 年英国团聚巡演门票</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-insists-oasis-will-be-as-good-as-they-once-were-and-they-will-still-wipe-the-floor-with-majority-of-bands-out-there-3811490">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 坚称 Oasis 将“像以前一样优秀”，并且“仍将与大多数乐队一较高下”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
