<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-festival-2025-tickets-buy-how-to-price-line-up-faq-3809687">本周开始发售，</a>长途汽车和套票将于周四（11 月 14 日）下午 6 点（格林威治标准时间）发售，标准票将于周日（11 月 17 日）上午 9 点（格林威治标准时间）发售。门票将<a href="https://glastonbury.seetickets.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>独家发售。</p><p>去年的 BST 海德公园演出阵容包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/full-line-up-announced-for-stevie-nicks-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-3765318">Stevie Nicks</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kylie-minogue-at-bst-hyde-park-2024-london-stage-times-3774511">Kylie Minogue</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/special-guests-announced-for-stray-kids-london-bst-hyde-park-show-3763729">Stray Kids</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/full-line-up-announced-for-sza-at-bst-hyde-park-2024-3760887">SZA</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/more-support-acts-added-to-kings-of-leons-london-bst-hyde-park-2024-show-3762832">Kings Of Leon</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-to-headline-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-buy-tickets-3598527">Morgan Wallen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hans-zimmer-seal-and-more-announced-as-special-guests-for-andrea-bocelli-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-3763248">Andrea Bocelli</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-to-headline-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-buy-tickets-3553493">Robbie Williams</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/full-line-up-announced-for-shania-twain-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-3764110">Shania Twain</a> 。</p><p>在其他地方，罗德里戈最近从<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/tiktok">TikTok</a>中删除了一首被<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>竞选团队使用的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-removes-song-from-tiktok-after-its-use-by-trump-campaign-3811207">歌曲</a>。</p><p>这位歌手一直是一位直言不讳的生殖权利活动家，今年早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-launches-reproductive-rights-initiative-the-fund-4-good-3592805">宣布启动 The Fund 4 Good 倡议，</a>作为